quran[64]{c,v,t}:
  84,1,Mohla leholimo le qhashohang ka lehare
  84,2,Le thea-tsebe ho Mong`a lona. Le tlamehile
  84,3,Ha lefats’e le batalatsoa
  84,4,"Le hlohlolla se ka hara lona, le sala le hlobotse"
  84,5,"Le thea-tsebe ho Mong`a lona, le tlamehile"
  84,6,"Oho motho! Ruri o khasetsa ho Mong`a hau, u khasa ka thata, – empa u tla kopana le Eena"
  84,7,Haele ea tla fuoa tlaleho ea hae ka letsohong la molema
  84,8,U tla be a tlaleha bobe
  84,9,"U tla retellehela ho ba habo, a thabile"
  84,10,Empa ea fuoang tlaleho ea hae ka morao
  84,11,O tla llela timelo
  84,12,O tla kena lelakabeng la mollo
  84,13,"Ruri! O phetse le beng ka eena, ka nyakallo"
  84,14,Ruri! O ne a nahana hore ha a na khutlela ho Rona
  84,15,"Che, che! Mong`a hae haesale a mo shalimme"
  84,16,Kahoo ke hlapanya ka mahlaseli a letsatsi ha le hlahlamela litaba
  84,17,Bosiu le tseo bo-ikapesitseng ka tsona
  84,18,"Le ka ngoeli, e tolokile"
  84,19,Le tla tsamaea sebaka le sebaka
  84,20,Molato ke’ng ka bona haele moo ba hloka tumelo
  84,21,"Ha ba balloa Qur`an, ba sa khumamele Allah"
  84,22,Empa mahana-tumelo a latola
  84,23,Empa Allah u na le tsebo e phahametseng ka tseoba li patang
  84,24,Kahoo u ba tsebise ka kotlo e bohloko
  84,25,"Kantle ho ba-kholoang, ba liketso tse lokileng; moputso oa bona oo ke keng oa thisa"
  85,1,Ka leholimo le linaleli tse jeroeng ke lona
  85,2,Ka le Letsatsi le Ts’episitsoeng
  85,3,"Ka ea pakang, le se pakoang"
  85,4,Ho malimabe baepi ba mokoti
  85,5,Mollo o beseletsoang
  85,6,Bona! ba ne ba tjamme pel’a ona
  85,7,Ke lipaki ho tseo ba neng ba li etsa khahlanong le ba-kholoang
  85,8,"Ba ba hlokofalitse kantle ho lebaka haese feela hore ba kholoa ho Allah, Ea Matla Oohle, U ts’oanetsoe ke Lithoriso tsohle"
  85,9,Eo `Muso oa maholimo e leng oa Hae le lefats`e! Allah ke Paki ea lintho tsohle
  85,10,"Haele ba hobosang ba-kholoang, banna le basali, ba sa retellehele ka boinyatso(ho Allah), ba tla fumana kahlolo ea Lihele: ba tla otloa ka mollo o tukang"
  85,11,"Ho ba-kholoang, ba etsang ketso tse lokileng, e tlaba lirapa tseo linoka li phallang tlasa tsona. Seo ke pholoho e babatsehang"
  85,12,Ruri letsoho la Mong`a hau le matla
  85,13,"Ke Eena Ea hlolang ho tloha mathomong, A boele A phete"
  85,14,"U ts’oarela ka mehla, U Tletse Lerato-le-Mohau"
  85,15,Mong`a Terone e Tlotlehang
  85,16,Moetsi oa tsohle tseo A li rerang
  85,17,Na pale ea mabotho e fihlile ho uena
  85,18,A Faro le a Ba – Thamud
  85,19,Empa mahana-tumelo a lula a latola
  85,20,Empa Allah U ba kopetse ka morao
  85,21,Che! Sena ke Qur`an e tlotlehang
  85,22,E ngoliloeng letlapeng e babaletsoeng
  86,1,Ka leholimo le moeti oa bosiu
  86,2,Keng se tla le hlalosetsa hore na moeti oa bosiu keng
  86,3,"Ke Naleli, e khanyang"
  86,4,Ha ho phefomoloho e hlokang molebeli
  86,5,Motho ha a nahane seo a hlotsoeng ka sona
  86,6,O hlotsoe ka lerotholi la there –
  86,7,Le kollang lipakeng tsa mahalapa le likhopo
  86,8,Ruri Allah U na le matla a ho mo phelisa
  86,9,Letsatsi leo liphiri li tlang ho utolloa
  86,10,Motho ha a na ba le matla kapa mothusi
  86,11,Ka leholimo le fanang ka pula
  86,12,Le ka lefats’e le petsohang
  86,13,Ruri! Lena ke lentsoe le arolang botle le bobe
  86,14,Ha se ntho ea papali
  86,15,"Haele bona, ba etsa morero"
  86,16,Le ‘Na ke loha leano
  86,17,Kahoo fana ka nyehlisetso ho mahana-tumelo; u ba fe phomolo ha nakoana